title.narrative: Sustainable Rural Water Supply and Sanitation Project

description.narrative: The project development objectives (PDO) are to assist the Kyrgyz Republic to (i) improve access to and quality of water supply andsanitation services in the Participating Rural Communities; and (ii) strengthen capacity of the Recipient's institutions in the water supply and sanitation sector.
